.message.slice(0, 80));\n            }\n          } else if (update.message?.text?.startsWith('/start')) {\n            // First-time setup: reply with chat id so the creator can copy it\n            const chatId = update.message.chat.id;\n            await sendText(\n              token, chatId,\n              `\ud83d\udc4b Hi! Your chat ID is <code>${chatId}</code>\\n\\nPaste this into Admin \u2192 AI Chatbot \u2192 Telegram Chat ID, then save.`\n            );\n          }\n        }\n      } catch (err) {\n        if (abortCtl.signal.aborted) break;\n        console.warn(`[telegram] poll error creator=${creatorId}:`, err.message);\n        await sleep(5000);\n      }\n    }\n    console.log(`[telegram] poll stop creator=${creatorId}`);\n  })", "is_member_call": false, "source_file": "C:\\Users\\jimi\\Documents\\APP\\Blog\\server\\services\\telegram.js", "source_location": "L113"}, {"caller_nid": "services_telegram_stoppolling", "callee": "get", "is_member_call": true, "source_file": "C:\\Users\\jimi\\Documents\\APP\\Blog\\server\\services\\telegram.js", "source_location": "L162"}, {"caller_nid": "services_telegram_stoppolling", "callee": "abort", "is_member_call": true, "source_file": "C:\\Users\\jimi\\Documents\\APP\\Blog\\server\\services\\telegram.js", "source_location": "L164"}, {"caller_nid": "services_telegram_stoppolling", "callee": "delete", "is_member_call": true, "source_file": "C:\\Users\\jimi\\Documents\\APP\\Blog\\server\\services\\telegram.js", "source_location": "L165"}, {"caller_nid": "services_telegram_escapehtml", "callee": "replace", "is_member_call": true, "source_file": "C:\\Users\\jimi\\Documents\\APP\\Blog\\server\\services\\telegram.js", "source_location": "L174"}, {"caller_nid": "services_telegram_escapehtml", "callee": "String", "is_member_call": false, "source_file": "C:\\Users\\jimi\\Documents\\APP\\Blog\\server\\services\\telegram.js", "source_location": "L174"}, {"caller_nid": "services_telegram_initfromdb", "callee": "require", "is